parameters:
\N<Hinata Aki> ...So you were back home... It's been a
while.
\N<Hinata Aki> Wow... It's really been a long time...

\N<Hinata Aki> ...Taro, you left this town right after
graduating.
\N<Hinata Aki> ...Have you gotten used to life over there?
\N<Hinata Aki> Y-You...your room is probably a mess, right?!

\N<Hinata Aki> Taro has always been bad at cleaning, so I
always...
\N<Hinata Aki> ...I guess it's fine to talk about that...

\N<Hinata Aki> ...Since you've finally come back, why don't
you take it easy?

\N<Hinata Aki> It's still the same old town with nothing
much happening, huh~ Ahaha...
\N<Hinata Aki> ...I should probably go back home soon.
It's a bother to come over this late...
